paragraphs.title: Daily Trading Value ($) per Trader
paragraphs.text:
%sql 

SELECT sum(price*volume) TradingValue, streaming_ticks.sender senderID, substring(banks.name,0,14) name 
FROM streaming_ticks join banks on streaming_ticks.sender=banks.id
group by sender, name order by TradingValue desc
limit 50

paragraphs.title: Top 10 Most Active Traders
paragraphs.text: %sql SELECT streaming_ticks.sender ID, substring(banks.name,0,15) Name, count(1) TradesExecuted FROM streaming_ticks TABLESAMPLE (1 PERCENT) inner join banks on streaming_ticks.sender=banks.id group by streaming_ticks.sender, Name order by TradesExecuted desc limit 10
